26#pragma once
27
28#include <wtf/text/WTFString.h>
29
30namespace WebCore {
31
32struct CacheQueryOptions {
33 CacheQueryOptions isolatedCopy() const { return { ignoreSearch, ignoreMethod, ignoreVary, cacheName.isolatedCopy() }; }
34
35 bool ignoreSearch { false };
36 bool ignoreMethod { false };
37 bool ignoreVary { false };
38 String cacheName;
39};
40
41} // namespace WebCore
